20From%20Punjab%20To%20Bay%20Of%20Bengal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi's%20pollution%20levels%20continue%20to%20be%20in%20the%20severe%20category%20forcing%20authorities%20to%20impose%20emergency%20measures%2C%20including%20traffic%20curbs%20and%20shutting%20schools.%20The%20drastic%20air%20quality%20is%20a%20result%20of%20a%20cocktail%20of%20factors%2C%20the%20chief%20contributors%20being%20vehicular%20emissions%20and%20smoke%20from%20crop%20burning%20in%20neighbouring%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENASA's%20Worldview%20satellite%20has%20captured%20how%20the%20toxic%20smog%20extends%20from%20Pakistan%20to%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal.%20The%20smog%20is%20coupled%20with%20a%20sharp%20rise%20in%20farm%20fires%20in%20North%20India%2C%20shows%20the%20satellite%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENASA%20data%20shows%20that%20the%20number%20of%20farm%20fires%20has%20seen%20a%20sharp%20rise%20since%20October%2029.%20The%20state%20saw%20a%20740%20per%20cent%20increase%20on%20October%2029%20with%201%2C068%20farm%20fire%20incidents%20-%20the%20highest%20in%20a%20single%20day%20in%20the%20current%20harvesting%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20air%20quality%20index%20as%20high%20as%20500%20in%20some%20areas%20on%20Wednesday%20morning%2C%20New%20Delhi%20has%20topped%20the%20chart%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20polluted%20cities%20for%20the%20last%20six%20days.%20Stage%204%20of%20the%20Graded%20Response%20Action%20Plan%20(GRAP)%2C%20a%20set%20of%20anti-pollution%20guidelines%2C%20has%20been%20invoked%20and%20diesel%20trucks%20and%20construction%20activities%20have%20been%20banned%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20asked%20the%20governments%20of%20Delhi%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Rajasthan%20to%20urgently%20discuss%20with%20the%20Centre%20how%20to%20stop%20the%20farm%20fires.%20The%20court%20has%20said%20it%20cannot%20allow%20this%20to%20become%20a%20political%20battle%2C%20stressing%20that%20the%20choking%20air%20quality%20is%20responsible%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bmurder%20of%20people's%20health%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699432920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F4ufndm4o_nasa-smog-satellite_625x300_08_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-pollution-air-quality-not-just-delhi-satellite-pics-show-smog-from-punjab-to-bay-of-bengal-4556744%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22New%20Delhi's%20pollution%20levels%20continue%20to%20be%20in%20the%20severe%20category%20forcing%20authorities%20to%20impose%20emergency%20measures%2C%20including%20traffic%20curbs%20and%20shutting%20schools.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-pollution-air-quality-not-just-delhi-satellite-pics-show-smog-from-punjab-to-bay-of-bengal-4556744%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-pollution-air-quality-not-just-delhi-satellite-pics-show-smog-from-punjab-to-bay-of-bengal-4556744%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-pollution-air-quality-not-just-delhi-satellite-pics-show-smog-from-punjab-to-bay-of-bengal-4556744%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2233%25%20Indian%20Women%20Can't%20Access%20Contraception%3A%20Outrage%20At%20This%2C%20Not%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20Words%20on%20Withdrawal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02190722%2FNitish-Kumar.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20constitutes%20an%20insult%20to%20the%20dignity%20of%20a%20woman%3F%20Ravaging%20her%20malnourished%20body%20to%20cause%20repeated%20pregnancies%20or%20talking%20about%20ways%20that%20she%20can%20avoid%20such%20a%20fate%20even%20when%20society%20and%20the%20government%20have%20failed%20in%20their%20duty%20to%20help%20her%20access%20contraception%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20questions%20are%20important%20when%20large%20sections%20of%20even%20the%20%E2%80%9Cliberated%E2%80%9D%20are%20outraged%20over%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20graphic%20description%20of%20withdrawal%20as%20one%20of%20the%20means%20that%20an%20educated%20woman%20can%20make%20her%20husband%20practice%20in%20order%20to%20avoid%20unwanted%20pregnancies.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiggling%20and%20blushing%20MLAs%20all%20around%20him%20%E2%80%93%20Kumar%20himself%20succumbs%20to%20a%20fit%20of%20laughter%20for%20a%20while%20%E2%80%93%20contribute%20to%20the%20trivialisation%20of%20an%20issue%20that%20has%20as%20much%20been%20India%E2%80%99s%20bane%20as%20the%20reluctance%20to%20address%20the%20root%20causes%20behind%20it%20without%20shame%20and%20manufactured%20outrage.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESex%20is%20a%20taboo%20word%20in%20a%20country%20that%20produces%2025%20million%20children%20every%20year.%20Safe%20sex%20is%20anathema.%20Talking%20about%20it%20in%20the%20assembly%20is%20sacrilege!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENational%20Family%20Health%20Survey%205%20(data%20from%202019-20)%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frchiips.org%2Fnfhs%2FNFHS-5_FCTS%2FIndia.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esays%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20only%2066.7%25%20Indian%20women%20have%20access%20to%20any%20method%20of%20contraception%20and%20just%2056.5%25%20have%20access%20to%20a%20modern%20method.%20(A%20modern%20method%20refers%20to%20sterilisation%2C%20contraceptive%20pills%2C%20condoms%2C%20intrauterine%20devices%20or%20injectable%20contraceptives.)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frchiips.org%2Fnfhs%2FNFHS-5_FCTS%2FBihar.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBihar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20numbers%20are%2055.8%25%20for%20any%20method%20and%2044.4%25%20for%20any%20modern%20method.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20description%20in%20the%20assembly%20is%20of%20withdrawal%2C%20a%20method%20where%20the%20man%20retracts%20before%20ejaculation.%20It%20is%20an%20accepted%20mode%20of%20contraception%20in%20any%20basic%20physiology%20textbook%2C%20albeit%20an%20unreliable%20one.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20total%20fertility%20rate%20%E2%80%93%20that%20is%20the%20average%20number%20of%20children%20that%20a%20woman%20would%20give%20birth%20to%20during%20her%20life%20time%20%E2%80%93%20stands%20according%20to%20NFHS%205%20at%203%20in%20Bihar%20while%20the%20national%20average%20stands%20at%202.2%20which%20is%20just%20a%20notch%20above%20the%20replacement%20fertility%20rate%20of%202.1.%20Replacement%20fertility%20refers%20to%20a%20situation%20where%20the%20population%20stops%20actually%20growing%20as%20death%20and%20birth%20rates%20reach%20a%20balance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20times%20immemorial%20governments%20in%20India%20have%20made%20family%20planning%20%E2%80%93%20euphemism%20for%20reducing%20births%20%E2%80%93%20their%20business.%20Yet%20if%2033%25%20Indian%20women%20and%2045%25%20Bihari%20women%20do%20not%20have%20access%20to%20any%20method%20of%20contraception%20that%20should%20be%20the%20cause%20for%20real%20outrage%20for%20all.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20squeamishness%20to%20talk%20about%20sex%20and%20the%20political%20backlash%20that%20anything%20akin%20to%20sex%20education%20invariably%20generates%20has%20given%20rise%20to%20a%20situation%20where%20Indian%20men%20get%20their%20sex%20education%20from%20pornography%20materials%20and%20women%20largely%20get%20it%20from%20life%2C%20learning%20the%20hard%20way%20about%20what%20can%20cause%20a%20pregnancy%20often%20ending%20up%20as%20unwitting%20victims%20of%20a%20system%20that%20is%20quick%20to%20punish%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnmet%20contraceptive%20needs%20lead%20to%20illegal%20abortions%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20need%20for%20contraception%20and%20sex%20education%20go%20beyond%20the%20need%20of%20limiting%20family%20size%20which%20in%20itself%20is%20a%20multilayered%20proposition%20with%20implications%20on%20health%2C%20education%2C%20economic%20status%20etc%20of%20a%20family.%20It%20is%20a%20question%20of%20life%20and%20death.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20her%20seminal%20book%20%3Cem%3EPutting%20Women%20First%3C%2Fem%3E%20based%20on%20her%20own%20gynaecology%20practice%20in%20Gadchiroli%2C%20Dr%20Rani%20Bang%20gives%20innumerable%20examples%20of%20women%20and%20girls%20%E2%80%93%20some%20of%20them%20as%20young%20as%2013%20%E2%80%93%20getting%20pregnant%20within%20weeks%20of%20menarche%2C%20sometimes%20not%20realising%20that%20they%20are%20pregnant%20till%20its%20too%20late%20to%20abort%20and%20then%20victimised%20by%20the%20tribal%20society%20for%20their%20%E2%80%9Cmistakes%E2%80%9D.%20In%20a%20telling%20statement%20on%20what%20lack%20of%20sex%20education%20does%20to%20young%20people%2C%20Dr%20Bang%20recounts%20the%20tale%20of%20a%20young%20boy%20who%20wrote%20her%20a%20letter%20addressing%20her%20as%20%E2%80%9Cauntie%E2%80%9D%20to%20talk%20about%20his%20own%20adolescent%20sexual%20insecurities%20and%20of%20a%20married%20couple%20who%20arrived%20at%20her%20clinic%20unsure%20about%20what%20constitutes%20the%20sexual%20act.%20She%20recounts%20countless%20cases%20in%20great%20detail%20of%20women%20and%20girls%20who%20had%20landed%20up%20at%20her%20clinic%20demanding%20an%20abortion%20past%20the%20legal%20timelines%20and%20then%20ending%20up%20either%20with%20an%20illegal%20abortion%20or%20worse%20still%20delivering%20an%20unwanted%20baby%20that%20is%20buried%20alive%20as%20per%20local%20practices.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20Population%20Fund%20(UNFPA)%E2%80%99s%20State%20of%20the%20World%20Population%20Report%202022.%20Between%202007-2011%2C%2067%25%20of%20abortions%20in%20India%20were%20classified%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Findia-unintended-pregnancy-abortion-7845655%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eunsafe%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Many%20of%20them%20happen%20first%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20contraceptive%20access%20and%20awareness%2C%20then%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20safe%20(and%20non%20judgemental)%20abortion%20facilities.%20Every%20day%20an%20estimated%208%20women%20die%20in%20India%20because%20of%20unsafe%20abortions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDr%20Bang%20is%20one%20of%20the%20founding%20members%20of%C2%A0%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsearchforhealth.ngo%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESociety%20for%20Education%2C%20Action%20and%20Research%20in%20Community%20Health%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(SEARCH)%20which%20runs%20a%20100%20bed%20hospital%20in%20Gadchiroli%20and%20has%20been%20a%20pioneer%20in%20many%20public%20health%20initiatives%20that%20have%20over%20the%20years%20been%20integrated%20into%20national%20programmes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20women%20are%20acutely%20aware%20of%20the%20importance%20of%20contraception%20and%20often%20at%20a%20loss%20about%20how%20to%20access%20it%20was%20evident%20when%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Flifestyle%2Fhealth%2Finjectable-contraceptives-at-mewat-women-get-shot-of-empowerment-5417216%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMewat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20categorised%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20backward%20districts%20in%20the%20country%20%E2%80%93%20immediately%20after%20the%20inclusion%20of%20injectable%20contraceptives%20in%20the%20National%20Health%20Mission%20basket%20saw%20women%20turning%20up%20at%20the%20clinics%20for%20a%20shot%2C%20often%20without%20telling%20their%20families.%20The%20women%20told%20me%20they%20wanted%20to%20put%20a%20stop%20to%20the%20cycle%20of%20annual%20pregnancies%20in%20which%20many%20of%20them%20were%20caught%20and%20as%20the%20local%20health%20workers%20talked%20to%20them%20about%20options%2C%20that%20of%20getting%20a%20shot%20that%20would%20prevent%20pregnancies%20for%20a%20period%20of%20time%2C%20was%20a%20godsend.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20speech%20in%20the%20assembly%20gives%20women%20access%20to%20one%20more%20method%20of%20contraception%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20rudimentary%20and%20primitive%2C%20it%20is%20worth%20more%20than%20a%20few%20laughs.%20The%20outrage%20can%20be%20reserved%20for%20more%20deserving%20causes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAbantika%20Ghosh%20is%20a%20former%20journalist%20and%20author.%20She%20currently%20works%20with%20Chase%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699432843000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02190722%2FNitish-Kumar.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fnitish-kumar-withdrawal-contraception-women%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20trivialisation%20of%20this%20issue%20has%20as%20much%20been%20India%E2%80%99s%20bane%20as%20the%20reluctance%20to%20address%20the%20root%20causes%20behind%20it%20without%20shame%20and%20manufactured%20outrage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fnitish-kumar-withdrawal-contraception-women%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22World%20Cup%3A%20Rain%20forecast%20adds%20uncertainty%20to%20NZ's%20clash%20with%20SL%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699432020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105063112%2Cimgsize-49698.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-world-cup%2Fnews%2Fworld-cup-rain-forecast-adds-uncertainty-to-new-ze