%20accepted%20bribes%20from%20Dubai-based%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20to%20ask%20questions%20in%20parliament%2C%20speaker%20Om%20Birla%20forwarded%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20ethics%20committee.%20This%20also%20meant%20he%20had%20to%20constitute%20the%20committee%20as%20it%20was%20not%20functional.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBirla%20formed%20a%2015-member%20committee%2C%20naming%20seven%20members%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20one%20from%20the%20pro-BJP%20Eknath%20Shinde%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20three%20from%20Congress%20and%20one%20each%20from%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%2C%20Yuvajana%20Sramika%20Rythu%20Congress%20Party%2C%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20(United).%20The%20committee%20was%20to%20be%20headed%20by%20BJP%20MP%20Vinod%20Kumar%20Sonkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EClearly%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20has%20the%20majority%20in%20the%20committee%20constituted%20to%20probe%20the%20complaint%20filed%20against%20the%20opposition%20MP%20who%20has%20not%20only%20been%20a%20vociferous%20critic%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20but%20had%20also%20openly%20accused%20the%20complainant%20Dubey%20some%20time%20ago%20of%20submitting%20what%20she%20claimed%20was%20a%20fake%20degree%20along%20with%20his%20affidavit%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission.%20Moitra%20has%20told%20reporters%20that%20Dubey%20filed%20the%20complaint%20against%20her%20because%20she%20inquired%20about%20his%20degree.%20The%20BJP%20MP%20has%20filed%20the%20complaint%20along%20with%20lawyer%20Jai%20Anant%20Dehadrai%20whom%20Moitra%20has%20termed%20as%20her%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3Ejilted%20ex%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoitra%20says%20the%20reason%20the%20ruling%20party%20is%20targeting%20her%20is%20because%20she%20has%20been%20asking%20the%20Modi%20government%20several%20uncomfortable%20questions%20about%20its%20alleged%20favouritism%20towards%20the%20Gujarati%20business%20tycoon%20Gautam%20Adani.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoitra%20says%20Sonkar%20has%20picked%20November%209%20as%20the%20date%20for%20the%20ethics%20committee%20meeting%20to%20ensure%20that%20a%20member%20of%20the%20committee%2C%20a%20Congress%20MP%20from%20Telangana%2C%20is%20unable%20to%20attend%20it.%20The%20MP%2C%20Uttam%20Kumar%20Reddy%2C%20is%20contesting%20the%20forthcoming%20Telangana%20assembly%20elections%20and%20has%20to%20be%20in%20his%20constituency%20to%20file%20his%20nomination%20papers%20on%20November%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20meeting%20of%20the%20ethics%20committee%2C%20five%20Opposition%20MPs%20including%20Reddy%20had%20walked%20out%20in%20protest%20against%20the%20chairperson%20asking%20Moitra%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3Eindecent%20questions%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20Moitra%20too%20had%20walked%20out%20in%20protest%20at%20the%20line%20of%20questioning%20which%20she%20said%20was%20equal%20to%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3EVastraharan%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ein%20the%20%3Cem%3EMahabharat%3C%2Fem%3E.%20She%20had%20put%20in%20her%20request%20to%20the%20chairperson%20to%20cross-examine%20both%20Dehadrai%20and%20Hiranandani%20who%20had%20submitted%20a%20%3Cem%3Esuo%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Emotu%3C%2Fem%3E%20affidavit%20to%20the%20committee%20claiming%20he%20had%20accessed%20her%20official%20email%20account%20to%20post%20parliamentary%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmahua-moitra-ramesh-bidhuri-very-different-parliament-committee%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Very%20Different%20Approach%20for%20BJP%20MP%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%E2%80%99%3A%20Mahua%20Moitra%20Writes%20to%20Parliament%20Committee%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20social%20media%2C%20Moitra%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20though%20the%20chairperson%20had%20announced%20that%20the%20November%209%20meeting%20would%20consider%20adopting%20a%20draft%20report%20on%20the%20complaint%2C%20no%20such%20report%20has%20been%20circulated%20among%20the%20members%20yet.%20She%20also%20added%2C%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3EBJP%20calling%20allies%20to%20ensure%20attendance%20to%20adopt%20(the%20draft%20report)%20via%20majority.%20Chartered%20flight%20to%20fly%20in%20MP(Madhya%20Pradesh)%20state%20president%20(V.%20D.%20Sharma).%20How%20scared%20Adani%20%26amp%3B%20Modi%20are.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDubey%20also%20took%20to%20X%20to%20claim%20that%20it%20was%20her%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3Eguilty%20conscience%E2%80%9D%20that%20has%20led%20her%20to%20worry%20about%20the%20panel%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENews%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fmahua-moitra-cash-for-query-case-ethics-panel-likely-to-recommend-strict-actions-including-disqualification-of-tmc-mp-11699233232862.html%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20said%20that%20the%20committee%20is%20likely%20to%20recommend%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3Estrict%20actions%E2%80%9D%20including%20her%20suspension%20from%20parliament%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAny%20decision%20by%20the%20committee%20would%20need%20to%20be%20endorsed%20by%20the%20speaker%20and%20would%20also%20be%20subject%20to%20judicial%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699431799000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F04145325%2F2022_2img03_Feb_2022_PTI02_03_2022_000159B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmahua-moitra-vinod-kumar-sonkar-ethics-panel-dehadrai%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20TMC%20MP%20has%20said%20November%209%20was%20picked%20as%20the%20date%20for%20the%20meeting%20so%20that%20a%20member%20of%20the%20committee%2C%20a%20Congress%20MP%20from%20Telangana%2C%20is%20unable%20to%20attend%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmahua-moitra-vinod-kumar-sonkar-ethics-panel-dehadrai%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Early%20Winter%20Break%20In%20Delhi%20Schools%20From%20November%209-18%20Due%20To%20Air%20Pollution%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDelhi%20schools%20will%20close%20for%20a%20winter%20break%20from%20November%209%20to%2018%20-%20in%20view%20of%20the%20toxic%20smog%20that%20has%20blanketed%20the%20city%20for%20six%20straight%20days%20-%20the%20city's%20Directorate%20of%20Education%20said%20Wednesday%2C%20noting%20%26quot%3Bno%20respite%20from%20adverse%20weather%20conditions%26quot%3B%20has%20been%20predicted%20over%20the%20next%20few%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20was%20taken%20at%20a%20meeting%20chaired%20by%20Environment%20Minister%20Gopal%20Rai%20and%20attended%20by%20Education%20Minister%20Atishi%2C%20Transport%20Minister%20Kailash%20Gahlot%20and%20senior%20Delhi%20government%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20bring%20forward%20the%20vacation%20-%20normally%20in%20December-January%20-%20was%20made%20to%20protect%20children's%20health.%20The%20Nov%209-18%20holiday%20will%20be%20adjusted%20against%20the%20traditional%20Dec-Jan%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Mr%20Rai%20had%20announced%20that%20all%20Delhi%20schools%20had%20been%20directed%20to%20suspend%20physical%20classes%2C%20except%20for%20those%20in%20Class%2010%20and%2012%2C%20till%20Friday%20due%20to%20alarming%20air%20pollution%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20is%20scrambling%20to%20contain%20the%20poisonous%20air%20hanging%20over%20residents'%20heads%2C%20but%20with%20little%20success.%20The%20AQI%20this%20morning%20was%20421%20-%20a%20sharp%20spike%20from%20395%20at%204%20pm%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20national%20capital%20region%2C%20Noida%20clocked%20in%20at%20409%20and%20Gurugram%20at%20370.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELevels%20of%20PM2.5%20-%20capable%20of%20penetrating%20deep%20into%20the%20respiratory%20system%20and%20triggering%20health%20problems%20-%20still%20exceed%20the%20government's%20limit%20of%2060%20micrograms%20per%20cubic%20metre%20by%20eight%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%2030-40%20times%20the%20limit%20prescribed%20by%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20anti-pollution%20measures%2C%20the%20fourth%20stage%20of%20a%20Graded%20Response%20Action%20Plan%20have%20been%20invoked%2C%20and%20(among%20other%20steps)%20diesel%20trucks%20and%20construction%20activities%20have%20been%20banned.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20had%20also%20announced%20the%20comeback%20of%20the%20odd-even%20rule%20-%20under%20which%20vehicular%20traffic%20is%20restricted%20based%20on%20the%20last%20digit%20of%20the%20registration%20number.%20The%20rule%20was%20to%20be%20re-instated%20for%20a%20week%20starting%20the%20day%20after%20Diwali%2C%20but%20there%20are%20now%20question%20marks%20over%20the%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20this%20afternoon's%20meeting%2C%20Delhi's%20ruling%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20said%20a%20decision%20on%20implementation%20of%20the%20scheme%20would%20only%20be%20taken%20after%20the%20top%20court's%20order%20is%20fully%20examined.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20-%20hearing%20a%20clutch%20of%20petitions%20on%20the%20air%20quality%20crisis%20-%20called%20such%20measures%20%26quot%3Boptics%26quot%3B%20and%20demanded%20the%20Delhi%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20governments%20to%20work%20together%20to%20contain%20and%20resolve%20the%20problem%2C%20with%20the%20focus%20(again)%20on%20farm%20fires.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20it%20(stubble%20burning%20leading%20to%20farm%20fires)%20stopped.%20We%20don't%20know%20how%20you%20do%20it%2C%20it's%20your%20job.%20But%20it%20must%20be%20stopped.%20Something%20has%20to%20be%20done%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20cocktail%20of%20factors%2C%20including%20vehicular%20emissions%20and%20stubble%20burning%2C%20are%20being%20held%20responsible%20for%20the%20air%20pollution%20in%20Delhi%2C%20where%20authorities%20have%20raised%20the%20pollution%20alert%20to%20the%20highest%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699431720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Flq2kling_delhi-smog-air-quality_625x300_03_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fearly-winter-break-in-delhi-schools-from-november-9-18-due-to-air-pollution-4556578%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20schools%20will%20close%20for%20a%20winter%20break%20from%20November%209%20to%2018%20in%20view%20of%20the%20toxic%20smog%20that%20has%20blanketed%20the%20city%20for%20six%20straight%20days%2C%20the%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20government%20said%20Wednesday%20afternoon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fearly-winter-break-in-delhi-schools-from-november-9-18-due-to-air-pollution-4556578%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fearly-winter-break-in-delhi-schools-from-november-9-18-due-to-air-pollution-4556578%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fearly-winter-break-in-delhi-schools-from-november-9-18-due-to-air-pollution-4556578%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Movies%2C%20series%20to%20watch%20before%20%E2%80%8BThe%20Marvels%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699431679000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105059380%2Cimgsize-101880.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fweb-stories%2Fthe-marvels-movies-and-web-series-to-watch-before-the-brie-larson-starrer%2Fphotostory%2F105059380.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105059380.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D