22%3Cp%3EPalestinian%20doctors%20and%20nurses%20who%20have%20stayed%20behind%20in%20Gaza%20Strip%20are%20heroes%20who%20know%20they%20are%20going%20to%20die%20but%20have%20chosen%20to%20stay%20anyway%2C%20a%20US%20nurse%20rescued%20from%20the%20Ground%20Zero%20of%20war%20has%20said.%C2%A0Emily%20Callahan%2C%20nurse%20activity%20manager%20with%20Doctors%20Without%20Borders%2C%20told%20CNN's%20Anderson%20Cooper%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fapp%3Ddesktop%26v%3Dgk7iWgCk14U%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20no%20safe%20place%20in%20Gaza%26quot%3B%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Callahan%20returned%20to%20the%20US%20over%20the%20weekend%20after%20being%20evacuated%20from%20Gaza%20last%20Wednesday.%20Asked%20how%20it%20feels%20to%20be%20back%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20obviously%20have%20a%20sense%20of%20relief%20that%20I'm%20home%20with%20my%20family%20and%20feel%20safe%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%2026%20days.%20(But)%20I'm%20having%20a%20really%20hard%20time%20finding%20any%20joy%20in%20any%20of%20it.%20Because%20me%20being%20safe%20is%20the%20result%20of%20having%20to%20leave%20people%20behind%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas'%20October%207%20terror%20attacks%20on%20Israel%20cities%20that%20left%20about%201%2C400%20people%20dead%20sparked%20a%20brutal%20counterstrike%20in%20Gaza%20Strip.%20The%20retaliatory%20attack%20has%20killed%20over%2010%2C000%20people%20in%20Gaza%20so%20far%2C%20according%20to%20UN%20estimates.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Callahan%20said%20they%20had%20to%20relocate%20about%205%20times%20in%2026%20days%20due%20to%20security%20concerns.%20%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20places%20we%20wound%20up%20was%20at%20the%20Communist%20Training%20Centre.%20There%20were%2035%2C000%20internally%20displaced%20people.%20There%20were%20children%20with%20just%20massive%20burns%20down%20their%20faces%2C%20necks%2C%20all%20over%20their%20limbs.%20Because%20the%20hospitals%20are%20so%20overwhelmed%2C%20they%20are%20being%20discharged%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDescribing%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20relief%20camps%20to%20shelter%20those%20displaced%20by%20Israel's%20airstrikes%2C%20Ms%20Callahan%20said%20a%20camp%20with%20over%2050%2C000%20people%20has%20four%20toilets%20that%20get%20water%20supply%20for%20four%20hours%20in%20a%20day.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20they%20have%20these%20fresh%20open%20burns%20and%20wounds%20and%20partial%20amputations%20walking%20around%20in%20these%20conditions.%20Parents%20are%20bringing%20their%20children%20to%20us%2C%20saying%2C%20'Please%20can%20you%20help%3F'%20And%20we%20have%20no%20supplies%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20nurse%20said%20they%20had%20to%20leave%20one%20of%20the%20camps%20because%20%26quot%3Bwe%20were%20starting%20to%20be%20harassed%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BDesperate%20people%20who%20are%20losing%20loved%20ones%20right%20and%20left%20are%20angry.%20And%20they%20would%20point%20at%20me%20and%20scream%20'American'.%20They%20would%20yell%20things%20in%20Hebrew%20to%20see%20if%20we%20were%20Israeli.%20They%20accused%20our%20national%20staff%20of%20either%20being%20traitors%20or%20said%2C%20'you%20are%20pretending%20to%20be%20Arab'%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Callahan%20said%20their%20Palestinian%20colleague%20stayed%20with%20them%20the%20whole%20time.%20%26quot%3BWe%20said%20to%20them%20that%20they%20don't%20have%20to%20stay.%20They%20said%2C%20'you're%20family%20too'%20and%20'we're%20not%20going%20anywhere'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20nurse%20said%20they%20would%20have%20died%20within%20a%20week%20if%20the%20local%20staff%20did%20not%20protect%20them.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20bombs%20going%20off%20all%20around%20us%20because%20there's%20no%20safe%20place%20in%20Gaza.%20They%20didn't%20leave%20our%20side%20for%20a%20second%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Rafah%20border%20crossing%20into%20Egypt%2C%20she%20said%2C%20it%20was%20the%20national%20staff%20who%20spoke%20to%20officials%2C%20got%20them%20onto%20buses.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20watching%20these%20incredible%20men%20who%20have%20sacrificed%20everything%20for%20us%2C%20who%20have%20sacrificed%20time%20with%20their%20families%2C%20their%20own%20physical%20safety%2C%20their%20own%20water%20supply.%20And%20we're%20watching%20them%20fight%20to%20get%20us%20across%20the%20border%2C%20knowing%20that%20we%20were%20not%20bringing%20them%20with%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20she%20would%20go%20back%20to%20Gaza%2C%20Ms%20Callahan%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20a%20heartbeat.%20My%20heart%20is%20in%20Gaza%2C%20it%20will%20stay%20in%20Gaza.%20The%20Palestinian%20people%20I%20worked%20with%20were%20some%20of%20the%20most%20incredible%20people%20I've%20met%20in%20my%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20nurse%20said%20that%20whenever%20she%20asked%20the%20national%20staff%20if%20they%20got%20out%2C%20the%20only%20answer%20was%20%26quot%3Bthis%20is%20our%20community%2C%20our%20family%2C%20these%20are%20our%20friends.%20If%20they're%20going%20to%20kill%20us%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20die%20saving%20as%20many%20people%20as%20we%20can%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Callahan%20said%20there%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Bidea%20being%20pushed%20right%20now%20that%20anyone%20that%20stayed%20behind%20is%20going%20to%20be%20considered%20some%20kind%20of%20a%20threat%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20remind%20people%20that%20people%20who%20stayed%20behind%20are%20heroes.%20They%20know%20they're%20going%20to%20die%20and%20they're%20choosing%20to%20stay%20behind%20anyway%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699430340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fi7j679tg_us-nurse_625x300_08_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-gaza-strip-50-000-people-4-toilets-water-4-hours-daily-nurse-