%20been%20identified%20as%20family%20members%20of%20a%20soldier.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESecurity%20forces%20rescued%20one%20of%20the%20kidnapped%20persons%20after%20the%20exchange%20of%20fire%20with%20armed%20men%2C%20who%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20abduction.%20At%20least%20nine%20people%2C%20including%20two%20policemen%2C%20have%20sustained%20injuries.%20Manglun%20Haokip%20(65)%2C%20who%20was%20rescued%20from%20kidnappers%20and%20sustained%20grievous%20injuries%2C%20has%20been%20admitted%20to%20the%20military%20hospital%20in%20Leimakhong.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20clue%20of%20the%20whereabouts%20of%20others%20until%20Tuesday%20evening%2C%20according%20to%20police.%20The%20Kuki-Zomi%20community%20organisations%20said%20the%20missing%20people%20include%20two%20women%20%E2%80%93%20aged%2060%20and%2055%20%E2%80%93%20and%20two%20men%2C%20aged%2040%20and%2025.%20They%20were%20abducted%20by%20armed%20men%20around%208%3A45%20am%2C%20close%20to%20Kangchup%20Chinkhong%2C%20which%20is%20at%20the%20border%20of%20Kangpokpi%20and%20Imphal%20West%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOn%2007.11.2023%2C%20at%20Kangchup%20Chingkhong%2C%20a%20Bolero%20carrying%20five%20individuals(2%20women%20and%203%20men)%20en-route%20from%20Churachandpur%20to%20Leimakhong%20was%20confronted%20by%20an%20enraged%20mob.%20The%20mob%20forcibly%20took%20away%20four%20of%20them%2C%20while%20one%20escaped.%20One%20person%20from%20the%20group%20was%20later%20rescued%20by%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Manipur%20Police%20(%40manipur_police)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmanipur_police%2Fstatus%2F1721977018101936457%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%207%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fabductions-gunfight-mark-tense-day-in-manipur-9017843%2F%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%3Cem%3E%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%E2%80%99%20Forum%20alleged%20that%20the%20Meitei%20radical%20group%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20was%20behind%20the%20abduction.%20The%20Forum%20urged%20central%20security%20forces%20to%20launch%20search%20operations%2C%20adding%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20fear%20they%20may%20have%20been%20killed%20or%20being%20tortured%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20incident%20was%20reported%20on%20Tuesday%20morning%20in%20the%20Kangchup%20Chingkhong%20village%20when%20five%20civilians%20in%20a%20Bolero%20car%20were%20stopped%20at%20a%20security%20checkpost.%20Soon%20a%20mob%20appeared%20and%20abducted%20the%20four%2C%20including%20two%20women.%20The%20central%20security%20forces%20deployed%20there%20could%20only%20rescue%20one%20of%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fmother-3-family-members-of-soldier-abducted-by-mob-in-manipur-father-injured%2Farticle67509763.ece%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20source%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Forum%2C%20Haokip%20was%20rescued%20by%20security%20personnel%20after%20attackers%20left%20him%20thinking%20he%20was%20dead.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20ensuing%20scuffle%2C%2065-year-old%20Manglun%20Haokip%20from%20Bolkot%20village%20was%20injured%20and%20fell%20unconscious.%20Thinking%20him%20dead%20the%20attackers%20left%20him.%20CRPF%20personnel%20later%20found%20him%20and%20transported%20him%20to%20Leimakhong.%20Due%20to%20the%20severity%20of%20his%20injuries%2C%20he%20has%20been%20airlifted%20to%20a%20neighbouring%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20Forum%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699428375000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15123624%2FF6AFowSaIAEUMh9.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-four-persons-including-kin-of-a-soldier-abducted-by-armed-men-from-kangchup-chingkhong%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Although%20the%20kidnappers%20took%20away%20five%20people%2C%20security%20forces%20rescued%20one%20of%20them.%20Of%20the%20five%2C%20four%20of%20them%20have%20been%20identified%20as%20family%20members%20of%20a%20soldier.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-four-persons-including-kin-of-a-soldier-abducted-by-armed-men-from-kangchup-chingkhong%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ketan%20Anand%20UPSET%20with%20IFFI%20organisers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699428017000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105060747%2Cimgsize-41264.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fchetan-anands-son-ketan-anand-upset-at-iffi-organisers-as-they-plan-to-screen-the-restored-version-of-haqeeqat-exclusive%2Farticleshow%2F105060468.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105060468.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%2054th%20IFFI%20will%20take%20place%20in%20Goa%20from%20November%2020%20to%20November%2028.%20The%20Indian%20Panorama%20has%20selected%2025%20feature%20films%20and%2020%20non-feature%20films%20to%20be%20showcased%20at%20the%20festival.%20In%20addition%2C%20three%20international%20restoration%20films%20and%20seven%20Indian%20restored%20films%2C%20including%20Haqeeqat%2C%20Guide%2C%20and%20Shyamchi%20Aai%2C%20will%20be%20screened.%20Ketan%20Anand%2C%20son%20of%20Chetan%20Anand%2C%20expressed%20surprise%20that%20Haqeeqat%20was%20restored%20and%20screened%20without%20his%20knowledge.%20The%20festival%20will%20also%20have%20special%20sections%20for%20visually%20and%20hearing%20impaired%20audiences.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fchetan-anands-son-ketan-anand-upset-at-iffi-organisers-as-they-plan-to-screen-the-restored-version-of-haqeeqat-exclusive%2Farticleshow%2F105060468.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Billionaire%20CEO%20Of%20Chinese%20Livestreaming%20Platform%20Goes%20Missing%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChen%20Shaojie%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20leading%20gaming%20live-streaming%20platform%20DouYu%2C%20has%20disappeared%20and%20has%20been%20incommunicado%C2%A0for%20nearly%20three%20weeks.%C2%A0According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Ftech%2Fbig-tech%2Farticle%2F3240523%2Fchinese-tech-executive-chen-shaojie-ceo-douyu-said-be-held-incommunicado-after-authorities-find-porn%5C%22%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%2039-year-old%20CEO%20has%20not%20been%20seen%20in%20public%20since%20October.%20Meanwhile%2C%20his%C2%A0colleagues%20are%20unaware%20of%20his%20whereabouts%20and%20are%20not%20able%20to%20get%20in%20contact%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20disappearance%20comes%20after%20authorities%20discovered%20pornography%20and%20gambling%20content%20on%20the%20platform.%20Local%20media%20reports%20say%20that%20Mr%20Shaojie%20was%20being%20investigated%20and%20has%20been%20held%20''incommunicado''%20by%20Chinese%20authorities.%C2%A0There%20has%20been%20no%20official%20confirmation%20of%20his%20detention%20but%20lengthy%20disappearances%20by%20senior%20executives%20in%20China%20are%20often%20followed%20by%20announcements%20they%20are%20under%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20company%20spokesperson%20told%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F11%2F07%2Fbusiness%2Fchen-shaojie-china-ceo-intl-hnk%2Findex.html%5C%22%3ECNN%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20its%20''business%20operations%20remain%20normal%2C''%20adding%20that%20it%20would%20announce%20''any%20significant%20news%20or%20material%20activities''%20in%20a%20''timely%20manner.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%20made%20his%20last%20public%20appearance%20in%20August%20when%20he%20spoke%20on%20the%20company's%20quarterly%20earnings%20conference%20call%20with%20financial%20analysts.%C2%A0The%20Chinese%20live-streaming%20service%20was%20listed%20on%20the%20Nasdaq%20in%202019%2C%20where%20it%20raised%20about%20USD%20775%20million%20in%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20share%20offerings%20by%20a%20Chinese%20company%20on%20Wall%20Street%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDouYu%2C%20often%20compared%20to%20Amazon's%20Twitch%20service%2C%20hosts%20interactive%20live%20streams%20of%20video%20games%20on%20its%20desktop%20and%20mobile%20apps%20while%20letting%20users%20chat%20in%20real-time%2C%20as%20per%20CNN.%20DouYu%20is%20backed%20by%20Tencent%2C%C2%A0a%20Chinese%20multinational%20technology%20and%20entertainment%20conglomerate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20CEO's%20unexplained%20absence%20comes%20as%20China%C2%A0has%20sought%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20perceived%20immoral%20content%20in%20the%20booming%20industry%2C%20launching%20probes%20into%20several%20top%20social%20media%20platforms%20and%20targeting%20prominent%20influencers.%C2%A0Several%20of%20China's%20leading%20financiers%20and%20businesspeople%20have%20fallen%20from%20grace%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20February%20this%20year%2C%20Bao%20Fan%2C%20the%20Chinese%20billionaire%20chairman%20of%20the%20investment%20bank%20China%20Renaissance%20went%20missing.%20Later%20in%20May%2C%20Chinese%20state%20media%20reported%20that%20Bao%20had%20been%20in%20the%20custody%20of%20the%20anti-graft%20agency%20since%20his%20disappearance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20boss%20of%20China's%20state-owned%20banking%20giant%20Everbright%20Group%2C%20Li%20Xiaopeng%2C%20was%20also%20arrested%20last%20month%20on%20charges%20of%20taking%20brib