ation%20control.%20I%20have%20also%20stood%20for%20women%20empowerment%20and%20women's%20development.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20contentious%20remarks%20were%20made%20as%20he%20explained%20why%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fbihar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBihar%3C%2Fa%3E's%20fertility%20rate%20has%20dropped%20from%204.2%20to%202.9%20per%20cent.%20However%2C%20the%20language%20was%20slammed%20as%20%26quot%3Bshameful%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3Bdisgusting%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bvulgar%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%C2%A0National%20Commission%20for%20Women%20chief%20Rekha%20Sharma%20demanded%20Nitish%20Kumar%20apologise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%20were%20seen%20as%20crude%20attempts%20to%20put%20the%20onus%20of%20population%20control%20on%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShortly%20afterwards%2C%20he%20faced%20down%20vociferous%20protests%20in%20the%20Assembly%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20are%20all%20of%20you%20making%20noise%3F%20I%20told%20you...%20you%20saw%2C%20the%20reporters%20asked%20me%20and%20I%20gave%20an%20explanation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20shouted%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20%26quot%3BI%20take%20my%20words%20back%2C%20%26quot%3B%20says%20Bihar%20CM%20Nitish%20Kumar%20as%20opposition%20leaders%20protest%20inside%20Bihar%20Assembly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FVbgolqAhYr%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FVbgolqAhYr%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1722130431079055806%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%208%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20row%20over%20the%20comments%20gathered%20pace%20yesterday%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%20was%20defended%20by%20his%20deputy%2C%20%