y.%20The%20OIC%20later%20announced%20that%20an%20extraordinary%20summit%20will%20be%20held%20in%20Riyadh%20on%20November%2012%20at%20the%20request%20of%20current%20chair%20Saudi%20Arabia%20to%20discuss%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20attacks%20on%20the%20Palestinian%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECertainly%2C%20the%20Iran-Saudi%20rapprochement%2C%20mediated%20by%20Beijing%2C%20has%20profoundly%20transformed%20the%20regional%20security%20environment%20with%20regional%20states%20preferring%20to%20find%20solutions%20without%20outside%20interference.%20Old%20schisms%20and%20xenophobia%20promoted%20by%20the%20US%20to%20perpetuate%20its%20dominance%20has%20no%20takers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20death%20toll%20in%20Gaza%20crosses%2010%2C000%2C%20feelings%20are%20running%20high%20in%20the%20Muslim%20world.%20Iran%E2%80%99s%20Supreme%20Leader%20Ali%20Khamenei%20said%20today%20that%20%E2%80%9Call%20the%20evidence%20and%20indications%20show%20the%20direct%20involvement%20of%20the%20Americans%20in%20running%20the%20war%E2%80%9D%20in%20Gaza.%20Khamenei%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F4308fe10-c037-4759-898b-1e5889871084%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F4308fe10-c037-4759-898b-1e5889871084%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1699496422598000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3X4L_crIyNWTbPWceXdiv9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0added%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20as%20the%20war%20goes%20on%2C%20the%20reasons%20behind%20the%20US%E2%80%99s%20direct%20role%20would%20become%20more%20explicit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Fars%20News%20Agency%2C%20which%20is%20close%20to%20the%20Islamic%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20Corps%2C%20also%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2F