%20in%20the%20north%20at%20any%20moment.%20We%20understand%20that%20it%20can%20happen%E2%80%A6%20We%20have%20a%20clear%20goal%20of%20restoring%20a%20significantly%20better%20security%20situation%20at%20the%20borders%2C%20not%20only%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENo%20power%20on%20earth%20can%20stop%20Israel.%20Its%20stability%20and%20defence%20are%20inextricably%20linked%20to%20this%20war%2C%20which%20will%20also%20ensure%20abiding%20US%20commitment%20to%20its%20security%20as%20a%20key%20template%20of%20American%20global%20strategies.%20Therefore%2C%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20best%20chance%20of%20survival%20lies%20in%20expanding%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza%20into%20Lebanon%20%E2%80%94%20and%20even%20Syria%20%E2%80%94%20shoulder%20to%20shoulder%20with%20the%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20question%20that%20locating%20the%20US%20nuclear%20submarine%20east%20of%20Suez%20is%20to%20intimidate%20Iran%20from%20intervening%2C%20while%20Israel%2C%20with%20US%20backing%2C%20opens%20a%20second%20front%20in%20Lebanon.%20The%20Israeli%20authorities%20have%20announced%20the%20evacuation%20of%20people%20from%20settlements%20up%20to%205%20km%20from%20the%20border%20with%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20war%20with%20an%20indeterminate%20timeline%20is%20set%20to%20begin%20in%20West%20Asia.%20There%20is%20no%20knowing%20how%20the%2080-year%20old%20American%20president%20will%20respond%20to%20the%20inevitable%20call%20of%20%3Cem%3Ejihad%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20this%20won%E2%80%99t%20turn%20into%20a%20world%20war.%20It%20will%20be%20fought%20in%20West%20Asia%20only%2C%20but%20its%20outcome%20will%20significantly%20impact%20the%20making%20of%20a%20new%20multipolar%20world%20order%2C%20after%20the%20precipitous%20decline%20of%20US%20influence%20and%20the%20volatile%20global%20environment%20since%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EM.K.%20Bhadrakumar%20is%20a%20retired%20diplomat.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%