l%20be%20organised%20in%20Yavatmal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20prominent%20OBC%20leaders%20met%20Maharashtra%20minister%20and%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(Ajit%20Pawar%20faction)%20Chhagan%20Bhujbal%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20November%207%2C%20in%20Mumbai%20to%20discuss%20the%20issue.%20A%20day%20earlier%20Bhujbal%20had%20struck%20a%20divergent%20note%20to%20that%20of%20his%20government%2C%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fchhagan-bhujbal-s-remarks-on-maratha-quota-created-confusion-shinde-sena-minister-101699404784157.html%5C%22%3Esaying%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20not%20tolerate%20injustice%20to%20OBCs%20and%20will%20not%20remain%20silent%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Eknath%20Shinde%20government%20has%20promised%20Marathas%20to%20complete%20the%20process%20of%20granting%20reservations%20by%20giving%20them%20OBC%20certificates%20and%20including%20them%20in%20the%20OBC%20Kunbi%20category%20by%20January%202%2C%202024.%20The%20move%20has%20angered%20OBC%20groups%2C%20which%20fear%20that%20Marathas%20would%20eat%20into%20their%20reservation%20pie%20of%2019%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20against%20increasing%20the%20EWS%20%5BEconomically%20Weaker%20Sections%5D%20quota%20and%20giving%20reservations%20to%20Marathas%20under%20it.%20But%20we%20are%20totally%20opposed%20to%20giving%20Kunbi%20certificates%20(under%20OBC)%20to%20all%20Marathas.%20We%20won%E2%80%99t%20tolerate%20all%20this%2C%20and%20will%20soon%20hit%20the%20streets.%20And%20if%20needed%2C%20we%20will%20also%20go%20to%20court%2C%E2%80%9D%20OBC%20leader%20Prakash%20Shendge%20said%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fmumbai%2Fobc-leaders-prakash-shendge-babanrao-taywade-maratha-quota-protests-9017845%2F%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShendge%20is%20also%20of%20the%20view%20that%20the%20Justice%20Shinde%20Commission%20formed%2