087.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Invests%20%24553%20Million%20In%20Adani%20Port%20In%20Lanka%20To%20Curb%20China's%20Influence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20will%20provide%20%24553%20million%20in%20financing%20for%20a%20port%20terminal%20in%20Sri%20Lanka's%20capital%20being%20developed%20by%20billionaire%20Gautam%20Adani%2C%20as%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Washington%20look%20to%20curtail%20China's%20influence%20in%20South%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20funding%20from%20International%20Development%20Finance%20Corp.%20underscores%20renewed%20US%20and%20Indian%20efforts%20to%20loosen%20Beijing's%20sway%20over%20Sri%20Lanka%20after%20Colombo%20borrowed%20heavily%20to%20splurge%20on%20Chinese%20port%20and%20highway%20projects%20before%20its%20economic%20meltdown%20last%20year.%20For%20Mr%20Adani%2C%20US%20money%20may%20offer%20a%20stamp%20of%20legitimacy%20after%20allegations%20of%20fraud%20by%20short%20seller%20Hindenburg%20Research%20erased%20billions%20from%20the%20conglomerate's%20market%20value%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20deepwater%20West%20Container%20Terminal%20in%20Colombo%20is%20the%20US%20government%20agency's%20largest%20infrastructure%20investment%20in%20Asia%2C%20and%20among%20its%20biggest%20globally.%20It%20will%20bolster%20Sri%20Lanka's%20economic%20growth%20and%20%26quot%3Bits%20regional%20economic%20integration%2C%20including%20with%20India%2C%20a%20key%20partner%20to%20both%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20DFC%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20funding%20is%20part%20of%20a%20global%20acceleration%20of%20DFC%20investments%20that%20totaled%20%249.3%20billion%20in%202023.%20A%20US%20official%20described%20the%20Sri%20Lanka%20port%20financing%20as%20emblematic%20of%20the%20US%20commitment%20to%20be%20more%20engaged%20in%20development%20projects%20across%20the%20Indo-Pacific.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChina%20had%20invested%20about%20%242.2%20billion%20in%20the%20island%20nation%20as%20of%20the%20end%20of%20last%20year%2C%20its%20biggest%20foreign%20direct%20investor.%20US%20officials%20have%20publicly%20criticized%20Sri%20Lanka's%20little-used%20southern%20Hambantota%20port%20as%20unsustainable%20and%20part%20of%20what%20it%20calls%20China's%20%26quot%3Bdebt-trap%20diplomacy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDFC%20said%20it%20will%20be%20working%20with%20sponsors%20John%20Keells%20Holdings%20Plc%20and%20Adani%20Ports%20%26amp%3B%20Special%20Economic%20Zone%20Ltd.%2C%20relying%20on%20their%20%26quot%3Blocal%20experience%20and%20high-quality%20standards.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EColombo's%20port%20is%20one%20of%20the%20busiest%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%20given%20its%20proximity%20to%20the%20international%20shipping%20routes.%20Nearly%20half%20of%20all%20container%20ships%20pass%20through%20its%20waters.%20The%20DFC%20said%20it's%20been%20operating%20at%20more%20than%2090%25%20utilization%20for%20two%20years%20and%20needs%20new%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20funding%20may%20serve%20as%20an%20endorsement%20for%20the%20short%20seller-stung%20Adani%20Group%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20controversial%20port%20project%20in%20which%20it%20holds%20a%20majority%20stake.%20The%20conglomerate%20has%20been%20fighting%20a%20raft%20of%20corporate%20fraud%20allegations%20leveled%20by%20Hindenburg%20Research%20and%20various%20media%20investigations%2C%20which%20it%20has%20repeatedly%20denied.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDFC%2C%20a%20development%20finance%20agency%20launched%20under%20the%20Trump%20administration%2C%20was%20established%20to%20aid%20developing%20nations%20while%20advancing%20US%20foreign%20policy%20goals.%20It%20struggled%20at%20first%20to%20stake%20out%20projects%20around%20the%20world%20due%20to%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20funding%20has%20accelerated%20in%20recent%20years%20and%20the%20agency%20has%20helped%20Washington%20close%20the%20development%20spending%20gap%20with%20China's%20much%20more%20higher-profile%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20report%20from%20the%20AidData%20institute%20at%20William%20%26amp%3B%20Mary%20in%20Virginia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20DFC's%20funding%20will%20create%20%26quot%3Bgreater%20prosperity%20for%20Sri%20Lanka%20-%20without%20adding%20to%20sovereign%20debt%20-%20while%20at%20the%20same%20time%20strengthening%20the%20position%20of%20our%20allies%20across%20the%20region%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Scott%20Nathan%2C%20the%20DFC's%20chief%20executive%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699422060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fi9oonteg_us-investment-in-adani-port-in-sri-lanka_625x300_08_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fus-invests-553-million-in-adani-port-in-sri-lanka-to-curb-chinas-influence-4556136%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20will%20provide%20%24553%20million%20in%20financing%20for%20a%20port%20terminal%20in%20Sri%20Lanka's%20capital%20being%20developed%20by%20billionaire%20Gautam%20Adani%2C%20as%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Washington%20look%20to%20curtail%20China's%20influence%20in%20South%20Asia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fus-invests-553-million-in-adani-port-in-sri-lanka-to-curb-chinas-influence-4556136%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fus-invests-553-million-in-adani-port-in-sri-lanka-to-curb-chinas-influence-4556136%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.