uth%20of%20Tel%20Aviv.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20Hamas%20attack%2C%20Israel%20has%20launched%20a%20withering%20air%2C%20ground%20and%20sea%20attack%20on%20Gaza%20to%20destroy%20Hamas%2C%20which%20has%20so%20far%20claimed%20more%20than%2010%2C300%20lives%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Hamas-run%20health%20ministry%2C%20in%20a%20month%20of%20gruelling%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch1%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Paradise'%20On%20Red%20Alert%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh1%3E%20%3Cp%3EShavit%20and%20Epstein%20met%20at%20a%20bar%20in%20April%202022%20and%20shared%20an%20%26quot%3Bimmediate%20attraction%26quot%3B%2C%20she%20remembered.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20finished%20their%20mandatory%20army%20service%20--%20she%20in%20military%20intelligence%2C%20he%20as%20a%20parachute%20regiment%20officer%20--%20before%20moving%20in%20together%20in%20the%20Kfar%20Aza%20kibbutz.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20commune%2C%20described%20by%20Shavit%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bparadise%20of%20trees%20and%20flowers%26quot%3B%2C%20they%20could%20see%20the%20buildings%20of%20Gaza%20City%2C%20the%20biggest%20urban%20centre%20in%20the%20long%20blockaded%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%20-%20October%207%2C%20the%20younger%20residents%20of%20the%20kibbutz%20were%20planning%20a%20group%20breakfast%20before%20a%20kite%20festival%20with%20a%20political%20take%20on%20the%20long-running%20dispute.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20wanted%20to%20fly%20them%20with%20messages%20of%20peace%20towards%20the%20Gaza%20border%2C%26quot%3B%20Shavit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20at%206%3A30%20am%20they%20were%20awoken%20by%20the%20words%20%26quot%3Bred%20alert%26quot%3B%20blaring%20over%20the%20kibbutz%20loudspeakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20alarm%20was%20routine%20in%20the%20border%20town%2C%20which%20has%20often%20been%20targeted%20by%20rocket%20fire%20from%20the%20Palestinian%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20took%20a%20selfie%20and%20sent%20it%20to%20their%20families%20