at%20the%20encroachment%20of%20the%20Himalayan%20ecosystem%20by%20road%20expansion%20and%20other%20construction%20activities%20will%20not%20bring%20any%20relief%20for%20the%20pilgrims%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20only%20imperil%20their%20safety%20and%20security%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKashmiri%20Muslims%20have%20always%20stood%20for%20the%20safety%20and%20welfare%20of%20the%20Hindu%20pilgrims%20who%20visit%20the%20shrine%20but%20such%20moves%20will%20have%20a%20devastating%20impact%20on%20our%20fragile%20environment%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tarigami%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EImran%20Dar%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20National%20Conference%2C%20said%20that%20the%20government%20should%20stop%20the%20%E2%80%9Cvandalisation%E2%80%9D%20of%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20seen%20how%20dangerous%20it%20can%20be%20when%20humans%20try%20to%20play%20with%20nature.%20The%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fnorth-india-rains-landslide-floods-toll%5C%22%3Enature%E2%80%99s%20fury%20in%20Uttarakhand%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20case%20in%20point.%20I%20hope%20the%20powers%20that%20be%20realise%20how%20sensitive%20these%20places%20are%20and%20stop%20such%20vandalisation%20of%20our%20mountains%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dar%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMohit%20Bhan%2C%20a%20Kashmiri%20Pandit%20and%20PDP%20spokesperson%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fbuttkout%2Fstatus%2F1721478721515987306%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Esaid%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20history%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20biggest%20crime%20one%20can%20commit%20to%20Hinduism%20and%20its%20faith%20in%20nature.%20Hinduism%20is%20all%20about%20immersing%20in%20spiritual%20mother%20nature%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20our%20pilgrimages%20are%20in%20the%20lap%20of%20the%20Himalayas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20prominent%20Kashmiri%20Pandits%20also%20criticised%20the%20road%20construction%20in%20the%20Himalayan%20region%2C%20arguing%20that%20the%20conversion%20of%20spiritual%20places%20into%20%E2%80%9Cconcrete%20jungles%E2%80%9D%20will%20have%20%E2%80%9Cdisastrous%E2%80%9D%20consequences%20for%20the%20Himalayan%20region%20where%20the%20vulnerabilities%20of%20climate%20change%20are%20already%20being%20felt%20by%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EQuestioning%20the%20motives%20behind%20the%20road%20construction%2C%20Kashmiri%20Pandit%20activist%20Satish%20Mahaldar%20said%20that%20the%20government%20is%20%E2%80%9Crefusing%20to%20learn%20the%20lessons%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20recent%20climate-induced%20disasters%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08103723%2FIMG_1574.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08103723%2FIMG_1574.jpeg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08103723%2FIMG_1574-300x222.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08103723%2FIMG_1574-1024x759.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684034%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20road%20to%20the%20Amarnath%20cave%20shrine.%20Photo%3A%20BRO%20video%20screengrab%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKedarnath%20was%20a%20real%20example%20where%20encroachment%20of%20natural%20ecosystems%20triggered%20nature%E2%80%99s%20fury%20and%20a%20humanitarian%20disaster.%20We%20saw%20how%20villages%20after%20villages%20sunk.%20Sadly%2C%20the%20government%20seems%20intent%20on%20bringing%20these%20disasters%20to%20Kashmir%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famarnath-cave-shrine-gets-motorable-road-amid-concerns-over-ecology-4552074%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BRO%20has%20completed%20the%20road%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20already%20approved%20a%20Rs%205300%20crore%20project%20for%20110-km%20four-lane%20highway%20to%20the%20holy%20cave%20shrine%20that%20also%20includes%20a%20major%20tunnel%20which%20will%20bore%20through%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20Himalayan%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Religious%20significance%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20proposal%20for%20a%20Detailed%20Project%20Report%20for%20Amarnath%20highway%20has%20been%20floated%20by%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Road%2C%20Transport%20and%20Highways%20but%20its%20Environmental%20Assessment%20Report%20has%20not%20been%20made%20public%20by%20the%20ministry%20yet%20which%20has%20said%20that%20it%20will%20cut%20down%20the%20pilgrimage%20time%20from%20two%20to%20three%20days%20to%20few%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUrging%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20%E2%80%9Crespect%20the%20sanctity%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Amarnath%20pilgrimage%2C%20Mahaldar%20said%20that%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20shorten%20the%20time%20for%20performing%20the%20pilgrimage%20by%20road%20construction%20will%20%E2%80%9Cruin%20its%20religious%20significance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPilgrims%20are%20supposed%20to%20halt%20at%20certain%20places%20on%20the%20yatra%20route%20and%20undertake%20some%20rituals%20which%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20done%20in%20a%20day%2C%20but%20it%20seems%20the%20government%20wants%20to%20turn%20this%20sacred%20pilgrimage%20into%20an%20adventure%20activity%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20officials%2C%20the%20project%20comprises%20a%2073-km%20stretch%20from%20Khanabal%20to%20Chandanwari%20in%20Anantnag%20district%20of%20south%20Kashmir%20worth%20Rs%201800%20crore%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20completed%20by%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%2010-km%20long%20tunnel%2C%20which%20will%20connect%20Pahalgam%20and%20Sonamarg%2C%20the%20second%20and%20the%20shorter%20among%20the%20two%20routes%20to%20the%20cave%20shrine%2C%20will%20be%20part%20of%20the%2037%20km%2C%20Rs%203500%20crore%20Chandanwari-Panjtarni-Baltal%20stretch%20of%20the%20highway.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20was%20a%20state%2C%20the%20two%20routes%20were%20maintained%20by%20local%20governments%20which%20were%20often%20under%20pressure%20from%20civil%20society%20activists%20and%20environmental%20groups%20to%20prevent%20a%20climate%20catastrophe%20at%20the%20cave%20shrine%20by%20limiting%20the%20footfall%20of%20pilgrims.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20more%20than%20dozen%20pilgrims%20were%20killed%20while%20several%20other%20pilgrims%20were%20injured%20when%20flash-floods%20hit%20a%20base%20camp%20near%20the%20cave%20shrine%2C%20prompting%20the%20authorities%20to%20suspend%20the%20pilgrimage%20indefinitely.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20after%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20in%202019%2C%20the%20routes%20were%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20BRO%20for%20maintenance%20which%20has%20been%20taking%20up%20expansion%20and%20repair%20activities%20before%20the%20start%20and%20after%20the%20culmination%20of%20the%20annual%20pilgrimage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20shrine%2C%20which%20sits%20at%20an%20altitude%20of%20over%2013000%20feet%2C%20houses%20an%20ice%20stalagmite%20that%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20an%20incarnation%20of%20Lord%20Shiva.%20The%20shrine%20was%20discovered%20by%20Bota%20Malik%2C%20a%20Muslim%20shepherd%20from%20Anantnag%20district%2C%20in%201850.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20shrine%2C%20which%20finds%20mention%20in%20modern%20and%20medieval%20records%20dating%20back%20centuries%2C%20was%20managed%20by%20Malik%E2%80%99s%20family%20till%202005%20when%20the%20shrine%20management%20board%20took%20control%20of%20the%20pilgrimage%2C%20pulling%20curtains%20on%20a%20decades-old%20practice%20that%20symbolised%20the%20essence%20of%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20syncretic%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699420136000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08103659%2FIMG_1571.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Famarnath-shrine-jammu-kashmir-ecology%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Kedarnath%20was%20a%20real%20example%20where%20encroachment%20of%20natural%20ecosystems%20triggered%20nature%E2%80%99s%20fury%20and%20a%20humanitarian%20disaster...Sadly%2C%20the%20government%20seems%20intent%20on%20bringing%20these%20disasters%20to%20Kashmir.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Famarnath-shrine-jammu-kashmir-ecology%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Patrick%20Dempsey%20Named%20People%E2%80%99s%202023%20Sexiest%20Man%20Alive%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699420108000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FGettyImages-1650627259-1.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D562%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235783627%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Patrick%20Dempsey%20is%20People%E2%80%99s%20sexiest%20man%20alive%20for%202023.%20The%20%E2%80%9CFerrari%E2%80%9D%20actor%20and%20%E2%80%9CGrey%E2%80%99s%20Anatomy%E2%80%99s%E2%80%9D%20Derek%20%E2%80%9CMcDreamy%E2%80%9D%20Shepherd%20was%20revealed%20as%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20honoree%20during%20Tuesday%20night%E2%80%99s%20broadcast%20of%20%E2%80%9CJimmy%20Kimmel%20Live.%E2%80%9D%20Prior%20to%20unveiling%20Dempsey%20as%20the%20sexiest%20man%20alive%2C%20the%20actor%20participated%20in%20a%20Q%26amp%3BA%20with%20the%20audience%20while%20wearing%20a%20realistic%20lizard%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fpatrick-dempsey-peoples-sexiest-man-alive-2023-1235783627%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fpatrick-dempsey-peoples-sexiest-man-alive-2023-1235783627%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fpatrick-dempsey-peoples-sexiest-man-alive-2023-1235783627%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20Who%20Is%20Rupi%20Kaur%20And%20Why%20She%20Declined%20White%20House%20Diwali%20Invite%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECanadian%20poet%20Rupi%20Kaur%20has%20declined%20an%20invitation%20to%20a%20Diwali%20celebration%20hosted%20by%20the%20White%20House.%20In%20a%20statement%20posted%20on%20social%20media%2C%20she%20said%20that%20she%20turned%20down%20the%20invite%20from%20the%20US%20government%20after%20their%20response%20to%20the%20ongoing%20Israel-Hamas%20War.%20The%20poet%20also%20urged%20other%20South%20Asians%20to%20demand%20accountability%20from%20the%20US%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Is%20Rupi%20Kaur%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3ERupi%20Kaur%20is%20a%20Toronto-based%20poet%2C%20author%20and%20illustrator.%20Her%20first%20book%2C%20a%20compilation%20of%20heart-warming%20poems%20and%20prose%20titled%20Milk%20And%20Honey%2C%20launched%20in%202014%2C%20sold%20over%20a%20million%20copies%20and%20reached%20number%20one%20on%20the%20New%20York%20Times%20bestsellers%20list.%20Her%20work%20focuses%20on%20themes%20of%20love%2C%20loss%2C%20trauma%2C%20healing%2C%20femininity%20and%20migration.%20The%20poet%20has%20over%20four%20million%20followers%20on%20Instagram.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20she%20was%20seen%20as%20an%20%26quot%3BInstapoet%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20she%20shot%20to%20fame%20after%20building%20up%20a%20huge%20follower%20base%20on%20social%20media.%20Ms%20Kaur%20came%20to%20the%20limelight%20when%20Instagram%20removed%20a%20self-portrait%20image%20of%20her%20that%20showed%20her%20sleeping%20on%20a%20bed%20with%20blood%20stains%20from%20her%20period.%20She%20took%20a%20stand%20against%20Instagram%2C%20calling%20attention%20to%20the%20duplicity%20of%20a%20platform%20that%20allowed%20women's%20sexual%20photos%20but%20restricted%20what%20it%20meant%20to%20be%20a%20normal%20female%20experience.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EControversy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Kaur%20declined%20a%20Diwali%20event%20invitation%20by%20the%20White%20House%20as%20she%20refuses%20%26quot%3Bany%20invitation%20from%20an%20institution%20that%20supports%20the%20collective%20punishment%26quot%3B%20of%20civilians.%20The%20event%20is%20scheduled%20to%20take%20place%20on%20November%208%20and%20is%20hosted%20by%20US%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Kaur%20also%20accused%20the%20US%20government%20of%20justifying%20%26quot%3Bgenocide%20against%20Palestinians%26quot%3B.%20In%20a%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCzUBPx8xwMp%2F%3Fimg_index%3D1%5C%22%3E%20post%20on%20social%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20received%20an%20invite%20from%20the%20Biden%20administration%20for%20a%20Diwali%20event%20being%20held%20by%20the%20VP%20on%20November%208.%20I%20decline%20any%20invitation%20from%20an%20institution%20that%20supports%20the%20collective%20punishment%20of%20a%20trapped%20civilian%20population-50%25%20of%20whom%20are%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%20The%20poet%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BToday%2C%20the%20American%20government%20is%20not%20only%20funding%20the%20bombardment%20of%20Gaza%2C%20they%20continue%20to%20justify%20this%20genocide%20against%20Palestinians-regardless%20of%20how%20many%20refugee%20camps%2C%20health%20facilities%2C%20and%20places%20of%20worship%20are%20blown%20to%20bits.%20They%20reject%20the%20call%20for%20a%20humanitarian%20ceasefire%20baseline%20action%20being%20demanded%20by%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20organizations%20like%20Doctors%20Without%20Borders%2C%20Red%20Cross%2C%20and%20a%20majority%20of%20countries.%20Over%2010%2C000%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed.%20The%20UN%20says%2070%25%20of%20the%20dead%20are%20women%20and%20children.%20We%20have%20seen%20Israel%20use%20white%20phosphorus%20bombs%2C%20which%20Amnesty%20International%20says%20must%20be%20investigated%20as%20a%20war%20crime.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20Celebrities%20Decline%20The%20Invite%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20South%20Asian%20personalities%20supported%20Ms%20Kaur%20and%20stated%20that%20they%20would%20also%20skip%20the%20event.%20Actor%20Richa%20Moorjani%20from%20Netflix's%20'Never%20Have%20I%20Ever'%20said%20she%20would%20boycott%20the%20celebration%20at%20the%20White%20House.%20%26quot%3BI%20stand%20tall%20boycotting%20White%20House%20Diwali%20with%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EContent%20creator%20Payal%20said%20that%20she%20had%20been%20waiting%20for%20an%20invitation%20since%20last%20year's%20event%2C%20however%2C%20she%20would%20decline%20hers.%20%26quot%3BI%20cannot%20in%20good%20faith%20attend.%20I%20cannot%20support%20this%20administration%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20cannot%20allow%20the%20darkness%20of%20their%20actions%20to%20be%20glazed%20over%20by%20beautiful%20glitzy%20outfits%20and%20photo%20opps...all%20to%20make%20them%20appear%20inclusive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIsrael-Hamas%20War%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israel-Hamas%20War%20began%20a%20month%20ago%20on%20October%207.%20As%20per%20Israeli%20authorities%2C%20more%20than%201%2C400%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20and%20240%20are%20held%20hostage%20in%20Gaza.%20The%20Gaza%20death%20number%20has%20soared%20above%2010%2C000%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20said%20the%20Hamas-run%20health%20ministry%2C%20as%20UN%20Secretary-General%20Antonio%20Guterres%20warned%20that%20the%20war-torn%20coastal%20strip%20was%20becoming%20a%20%26quot%3Bgraveyard%20for%20children%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20vowed%20to%20destroy%20the%20Islamist%20operatives%20over%20their%20unprecedented%20attack%20which%20witnessed%20entire%20families%20killed%20inside%20their%20homes%20and%20young%20people%20killed%20at%20a%20music%20festival%2C%20according%20to%20Israeli%20officials.%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20said%20Israel%20would%20consider%20%26quot%3Btactical%20little%20pauses%26quot%3B%20in%20Gaza%20fighting%20to%20facilitate%20the%20entry%20of%20aid%20or%20the%20exit%20of%20hostages%2C%20but%20again%20rejected%20calls%20for%20a%20general%20ceasefire%20despite%20growing%20international%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20told%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20in%20a%20call%20on%20Monday%20that%20a%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbiden-tells-netanyahu-3-day-ceasefire-could-help-secure-release-of-hostages-report-4555752%5C%22%3E%20three-day%20fighting%20pause%20could%20help%20secure%20the%20release%20of%20some%20hostages%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20a%20statement%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20White%20House%20said%20Mr%20Biden%20and%20Mr%20Netanyahu%20discussed%20%26quot%3Bthe%20possibility%20of%20tactical%20pauses%20to%20provide%20civilians%20with%20opportunities%20to%20safely%20depart%20from%20areas%20of%20ongoing%20fighting%2C%20to%20ensure%20assistance%20is%20reaching%20civilians%20in%20need%2C%20and%20to%20enable%20potential%20hostage%20releases.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699420080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Ffsge2g38_rupikaur_625x300_08_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-palestine-gaza-explained-who-is-rupi-kaur-and-why-did-she-decline-white-house-diwali-invite-4556072%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rupi%20Kaur%20declined%20a%20Diwali%20event%20invitation%20by%20the%20White%20House%20as%20she%20refuses%20%26quot%3Bany%20invitation%20from%20an%20institution%20that%20supports%20the%20collective%20punishment%26quot%3B%20