o.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67353115.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%20Farmers%20Are%20Timing%20Crop%20Burning%20To%20Avoid%20Detection%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFarmers%20in%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20are%20burning%20stubble%20at%20night%20to%20evade%20detection%20by%20satellite%20and%20local%20officials%20working%20overtime%20to%20contain%20farm%20fires%20that%20have%20poisoned%20the%20air%20in%20Delhi%20NCR%2C%20it%20is%20learnt.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20official%20data%2C%20incidents%20of%20farm%20fires%20have%20reduced%20this%20year.%20Between%20September%2015%20and%20November%207%20this%20year%2C%20nearly%2021%2C000%20farm%20fires%20have%20been%20reported%20in%20Punjab.%20This%20is%20a%20drop%20of%20about%2030%20per%20cent%20when%20compared%20to%20the%20same%20period%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20numbers%2C%20however%2C%20do%20not%20add%20up%20when%20seen%20against%20the%20number%20of%20paddy%20farmers.%20For%20example%2C%20over%2056%2C000%20farmers%20harvested%20paddy%20in%20Punjab's%20Ludhiana%20but%20less%20than%20a%201%2C000%20farm%20fires%20were%20reported.%20This%20indicates%20that%20many%20farm%20fires%20incidents%20are%20going%20undetected.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20could%20be%20happening%20because%20the%20daily%20farm%20fires%20count%20has%20to%20be%20updated%20by%208%20pm.%20The%20farmers%2C%20aware%20of%20this%20loophole%2C%20are%20setting%20fire%20to%20the%20fields%20after%208%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Haryana%2C%20the%20Haryana%20Space%20Applications%20Centre%20is%20using%20satellite%20imaging%20to%20detect%20farm%20fires.%20This%20imaging%2C%20however%2C%20is%20not%20conducted%20round%20the%20clock.%20Dr%20Sultan%20Singh%2C%20HARSAC%20director%2C%20has%20told%20The%20Tribune%20that%20the%20satellite%20imaging%20was%20carried%20out%20at%2012-hour%20intervals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20fires%2C%20therefore%2C%20may%20slip%20through%20the%20radar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20a%20section%20of%20farmers%20in%20Haryana%20believes%20that%20burning%20crop%20residue%20after%20sunset%20may%20help%20them%20evade%20detection%20by%20satellite.%20These%20farmers%20argue%20that%20satellite%20imaging%20uses%20temperature%20for%20detection%20of%20farm%20fires%20incidents%2C%20so%20the%20drop%20in%20temperature%20at%20night%20may%20lead%20to%20the%20satellite%20failing%20to%20identify%20farm%20fires.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Singh%2C%20however%2C%20dismissed%20this.%20%26quot%3BThe%20satellites%20detect%20farm%20fires%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20variation%20in%20temperature%2C%20which%20can%20take%20place%20at%20any%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20The%20Tribune.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJaswant%20Singh%2C%20director%20for%20agriculture%20and%20farmers'%20welfare%20in%20Punjab%2C%20too%2C%20said%20it%20is%20a%20baseless%20rumour%20that%20satellite%20imagery%20does%20not%20detect%20farm%20fire%20incidents%20at%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUndetected%20farm%20fires%20lead%20to%20mismatch%20in%20data.%20This%20is%20critical%20as%20government%20authorities%20are%20fine-tuning%20their%20strategy%20based%20on%20the%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%2C%20which%20rules%20both%20Punjab%20and%20Delhi%2C%20has%20said%20there%20has%20been%20a%20huge%20drop%20in%20the%20incidents%20of%20farm%20fires%20in%20Punjab%20and%20blamed%20vehicle%20emissions%20in%20BJP-ruled%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Haryana%20for%20Delhi's%20bad%20air%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20hit%20back%2C%20accusing%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20of%20turning%20the%20national%20capital%20into%20a%20%26quot%3Bcity%20of%20smoke%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20air%20quality%20index%20in%20Delhi%20remaining%20in%20the%20'severe'%20category%20for%20the%20past%20several%20days%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20asked%20the%20governments%20of%20Delhi%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Rajasthan%20to%20urgently%20discuss%20with%20the%20Centre%20how%20to%20stop%20farm%20fires.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20has%20said%20it%20cannot%20allow%20this%20to%20become%20a%20political%20battle%2C%20stressing%20that%20the%20choking%20air%20quality%20is%20responsible%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bmurder%20of%20people's%20health%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699419480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fmt5iero8_punjab-farm-fires_625x300_08_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-air-pollution-stubble-burning-delhi-air-toxic-but-data-shows-lesser-farm-fires-this-year-heres-why-4556011%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Farmers%20in%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20are%20burning%20stubble%20at%20night%20to%20evade%20detection%20by%20satellite%20and%20local%20officials%20working%20overtime%20to%20contain%20farm%20fires%20that%20have%20poisoned%20the%20air%20in%20Delhi%20NCR%2C%20it%20is%20learnt.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-air-pollution-stubble-burning-delhi-air-toxic-but-data-shows-lesser-farm-fires-this-year-heres-why-4556011%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-air-pollution-stubble-burning-delhi-air-toxic-but-data-shows-lesser-farm-fires-this-year-heres-why-4556011%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-air-pollution-stubble-burning-delhi-air-toxic-but-data-shows-lesser-farm-fires-this-year-heres-why-4556011%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ishaan%20on%20voicing%20Ravan%3A%20'It%20was%20fascinating'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699419422000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105057033%2Cimgsize-22728.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fishaan-khatter-on-voicing-ravan-in-an-audio