s%20in%202019.%20This%20time%20around%2C%20he%20is%20being%20fielded%20from%20the%20Kaman%20constituency%20as%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsked%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20why%20all%20six%20BSP%20MLAs%20decided%20to%20join%20the%20Congress%2C%20Ali%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%202018%2C%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20that%20the%20party%20was%20working%20for%20the%20BJP.%20However%2C%20a%20year%20later%2C%20when%20the%20party%20decided%20to%20field%20candidates%20in%20a%20way%20that%20benefited%20the%20BJP%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20quit%20and%20join%20the%20Congress.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%20190%20seats%20where%20the%20BSP%20contested%20elections%2C%20the%20party%20received%20a%20total%20of%201%2C435%2C858%20votes%20in%20the%20state%2C%20accounting%20for%204.03%25%20of%20the%20total%20vote%20share.%20However%2C%20in%20178%20seats%2C%20the%20party%20had%20to%20forfeit%20the%20security%20deposit.%20A%20candidate%E2%80%99s%20security%20deposit%20is%20liable%20to%20be%20forfeited%20if%20they%20receive%20less%20than%201%2F6th%20of%20the%20total%20valid%20votes%20polled.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20the%20BSP%20contested%20195%20seats%20in%20Rajasthan.%20The%20party%20won%20only%20three%20seats%2C%20and%20forfeited%20the%20deposit%20in%20182.%20Its%20vote%20share%20was%203.48%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202008%2C%20the%20BSP%20contested%20199%20seats%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20winning%20six%20and%20forfeiting%20the%20deposit%20in%20172.%20It%20received%207.66%25%20of%20the%20polled%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bipolar%20politics%20of%20Rajasthan%2C%20which%20has%20persisted%20since%201952%2C%20has%20weathered%20at%20least%20a%20dozen%20attempts%20to%20develop%20a%20third%20front%20in%20the%20state.%20These%20%E2%80%98third%20options%E2%80%99%20typically%20lasted%20for%20a%20decade%20or%20a%20couple%20of%20assembly%20polls%20at%20the%20most%2C%20before%20merging%20into%20one%20of%20the%20two%20main%20parties%2C%20le