d%20into%20a%20job%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it's%20not%20just%20jobs%3A%20Internships%20are%20proving%20elusive%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D27be19d99cde9d72347dc9b1a9a6d9fd10a0363f1167aaf8ef173305d5570663%26postID%3D652f8cb1cb790ff8bec0249e%26postSlug%3Dcomputer-science-major-myth-job-security-money-salary-2023-11%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.linkedin.com%252Fin%252Fbryan-ho-7271b91b4%252F%5C%22%3EBryan%20Ho%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%2023-year-old%20junior%20studying%20computer%20science%20at%20the%20National%20University%20of%20Singapore%2C%20told%20Insider%20he's%20applied%20for%20roughly%20100%20internships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20definitely%20become%20harder%20because%20if%20so%20many%20companies%20are%20cutting%20jobs%2C%20they%20will%20not%20take%20as%20many%20interns%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ho.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20his%20100%20applications%2C%20Ho%20said%20he%20received%20four%20offers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bryan%20Ho%2C%2022.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654349773cc84b4dfafa90d7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22721%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBryan%20Ho%2C%2022%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20he%20has%20applied%20for%20roughly%20100%20internships%20and%20received%20four%20offers.%3Cp%3EBryan%20Ho%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EToo%20many%20students%20chasing%20the%20same%20jobs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D7560bd26065f04b159a14d21a7ced7770a7e758e0929938c0ff2ce5711782e22%26postID%3D652f8cb1cb790ff8bec0249e%26postSlug%3Dcomputer-science-major-myth-job-security-money-salary-2023-11%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.linkedin.com%252Fin%252Fethanajx%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEthan%20Ang%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22