rchandise%20that%20can%20put%20profits%20right%20into%20your%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20you%20are%20interested%20in%20using%20Amazon%20Business%20as%20the%20chief%20supplier%20for%20your%20workplace%20or%20you%20are%20primarily%20interested%20in%20working%20with%20Amazon%20as%20a%20seller%20yourself%2C%20this%20guide%20can%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20much%20does%20Amazon%20Business%20cost%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20or%20someone%20at%20a%20managerial%20level%20in%20your%20company%20already%20uses%20Amazon%20Prime%2C%20then%20you%20can%20sign%20up%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Famazon-adds-business-prime-duo-as-free-offer-for-small-business-owners-with-prime-membership-1032411774%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Prime%20Duo%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20subscription%20gives%20the%20party%20that%20joins%20access%20to%20all%20the%20many%20benefits%20of%20Amazon%20Business%2C%20from%20low%20prices%20on%20office%20supplies%20to%20fast%20and%20free%20shipping%20of%20said%20materials.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20more%20people%20in%20the%20office%20to%20access%20Amazon%20Business%2C%20you%20can%20open%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-adds-perks-business-prime-2018-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Prime%20Essentials%3C%2Fa%3E%20account.%20That%20costs%20%24179%20annually%20and%20gives%20three%20people%20access%20to%20Amazon%20Business.%20No%20Prime%20account%20is%20required%20for%20Business%20Prime%20Essentials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESlightly%20larger%20operations%20can%20sign%20up%20for%20the%20%26quot%3BSmall%26quot%3B%20plan%20for%20%24499%2C%20which%20lets%2010%20users%20access%20the%20Amazon%20Business%20account.%20A%20%26quot%3BMedium%26quot%3B%20subscription%20costs%20%241%2C299%20and%20allows%20up%20to%20100%20users%20to%20share%20access.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20an%20%26quot%3BEnterprise%26quot%3B%20account%20allows%20more%20than%20100%20people%20from%20a%20given%20company%20to%20use%20Amazon%20Business.%20Also%2C%20it%20opens%20up%20access%20to%20what%20Amazon%20calls%20%26quot%3BOptimal%20Deployment%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20it%20describes%20as%20a%20way%20to%20%26quot%3Bachieve%20optimal%20visibility%20and%20policy%20settings%20via%20your%20Business%20Prime%20features%20with%20expert%20assistance%20from%20Amazon%20Business%20Professional%20Services.%26quot%3B%20That%20option%20costs%20%2410%2C099%20per%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20an%20Amazon%20business%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Amazon%20Business%20is%2C%20ironically%2C%20quite%20distinct%20from%20Amazon%20Business.%20Whereas%20the%20latter%20is%20a%20subset%20of%20Amazon%20itself%2C%20from%20which%20you%20buy%20office%20supplies%2C%20janitorial%20goods%2C%20IT%20hardware%2C%20and%20more%2C%20the%20former%20is%20a%20business%20making%20money%20by%20selling%20merchandise%20with%20the%20support%20of%20Amazon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20sell%20products%20via%20Amazon%2C%20you%20get%20the%20advantage%20of%20the%20company's%20vast%20network%20of%20potential%20buyers.%20Amazon%20offers%20your%20business%20%E2%80%94%20be%20it%20just%20you%20and%20your%20computer%20or%20you%20and%20your%20team%20of%20three%20dozen%20employees%20who%20have%20been%20running%20brick-and-mortar%20operations%20for%20years%20%E2%80%94%20amazing%20opportunities%20to%20get%20eyes%20on%20your%20products%20and%20to%20convert%20those%20views%20into%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20when%20you%20do%20make%20sales%20with%20Amazon%20Business%2C%20you%20have%20options%20for%20how%20you%20want%20to%20fulfill%20those%20orders%2C%20too.%20We'll%20get%20to%20that%20in%20a%20moment.%20For%20now%2C%20know%20that%20Amazon%20Business%20is%20a%20B2B%20setup%2C%20meaning%20a%20business-to-business%20arrangement%2C%20namely%20itself%20being%20in%20an%20arrangement%20with%20you.%20You%20partner%20with%20Amazon%20and%20use%20many%20of%20their%20services%20while%20you%20sell%20your%20products%20via%20Amazon%20to%20customers%20all%20around%20the%20nation%20or%20even%20around%20the%20globe.%3Cstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20does%20Amazon%20Business%20do%20for%20me%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20short%20story%20is%20that%20Amazon%20Business%20can%20save%20your%20workplace%20money%20on%20essential%20supplies%20and%2For%20can%20connect%20you%20to%20countless%20potential%20customers%20for%20your%20products.%20The%20longer%20story%20is%20that%2C%20depending%20on%20which%20Business%20Prime%20plan%20you%20select%2C%20Amazon%20Business%20offers%20you%20survey%20and%20analytical%20tools%20that%20can%20help%20you%20track%20your%20conversions%20and%20sales%2C%20study%20customer%20behavior%20and%20trends%2C%20and%20help%20boost%20revenue%3B%20it%20offers%20Amazon%20WorkDocs%2C%20which%20includes%20templates%20for%20things%20like%20invoices%20and%20sales%20receipts%3B%20it%20offers%20you%20buying%20guidance%20that%20will%20help%20you%20make%20the%20most%20of%20your%20office%20supply%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20and%20several%20other%20services%20can%20allow%20even%20smaller%20businesses%20to%20run%20with%20the%20efficiency%20of%20a%20much%20larger%20operation%2C%20as%20much%20of%20the%20work%20usually%20handled%20by%20a%20full%20HR%20department%20is%20managed%20by%20Amazon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20difference%20between%20Amazon%20and%20Amazon%20Business%20is%20that%20the%20former%20refers%20to%20the%20company's%20general%20online%20retail%20wing%2C%20whereas%20the%20latter%20refers%20either%20to%20sales%20of%20products%20specifically%20oriented%20toward%20workplaces%20or%20to%20the%20partnership%20you%20can%20set%20up%20with%20Amazon%20as%20you%20sell%20products%20yourself.%20Amazon%20and%20Amazon%20Business%20are%20not%20distinct%20entities%2C%20but%20they%20are%20separate%20divisions%20of%20the%20same%20company.%3Cstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20you%20need%20an%20LLC%20for%20Amazon%20Business%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20do%20not%20need%20to%20have%20an%20LLC%2C%20or%20limited%20liability%20corporation%20to%20start%20an%20Amazon%20business%20and%20to%20start%20selling%20via%20Amazon.%20A%20sole%20proprietorship%20wherein%20you%20are%20the%20business%20entity%20is%20perfectly%20acceptable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20your%20business%20grows%2C%20getting%20an%20LLC%20is%20wise%2C%20though.%20In%20many%20states%2C%20you%20can%20file%20for%20an%20LLC%20for%20less%20than%20%24100%2C%20while%20in%20others%2C%20the%20cost%20is%20somewhat%20higher.%20An%20LLC%20can%20help%20protect%20your%20personal%20wealth%20and%20assets%20should%20anyone%20ever%20take%20legal%20action%20against%20your%20company.%3Cstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20much%20money%20should%20you%20have%20to%20start%20an%20Amazon%20business%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20long%20as%20you%20have%20enough%20money%20to%20purchase%20and%20ship%20a%20single%20product%2C%20you%20can%20technically%20start-up%20as%20a%20seller%20on%20Amazon.%20But%20if%20you%20plan%20to%20move%20any%20appreciable%20product%20with%20Amazon%20Business%2C%20the%20general%20rule%20is%20to%20have%20%2410%2C000%20on%20hand%20if%20you'll%20use%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-fba%5C%22%3EAmazon%20FBA%3C%2Fa%3E%20seller%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFBA%20means%20%26quot%3Bfulfilled%20by%20Amazon%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20this%20is%20an%20arrangement%20where%20you%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-warehouse-empire-impact-us-economy-workforce-2022-10%5C%22%3EAmazon%20warehouse%3C%2Fa%3E%20your%20goods%20for%20you%20and%20handle%20the%20shipping%20whenever%20orders%20come%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20costs%20of%20an%20FBA%20arrangement%20can%20be%20pricey%2C%20as%20you%20pre-buy%20a%20lot%20of%20merchandise%20