imes%20gets%20talking%20to%20the%20children%2C%20and%20these%20conversations%20are%20life-changing%2C%20she%20notes.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20come%20from%20underprivileged%20backgrounds%2C%20and%20it%20is%20extremely%20moving%20to%20me%20how%20they%20can%20channel%20their%20energies%20into%20such%20beautiful%20coordinated%20dances.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20her%20students%20Saumya%20from%20Class%205%20says%20she%20has%20a%20hard%20time%20choosing%20between%20dance%20and%20art.%20She%20loves%20both.%20%E2%80%9CI%20love%20the%20colour-mixing%20process%20in%20art%20and%20have%20used%20it%20to%20make%20so%20many%20colourful%20leaf%20paintings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Taarush%20celebrated%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329782%2Fassam-school-accepts-plastic-as-fees-teaches-them-to-recycle-and-upcycle-pictures%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuccess%20of%20this%20model%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20his%20mind%20was%20already%20brewing%20with%20ideas%20for%20his%20next%20venture.%20He%20recognised%20the%20importance%20of%20equipping%20children%20with%20skills%20that%20would%20shape%20them%20into%20well-rounded%20individuals%2C%20enabling%20them%20to%20succeed%20in%20various%20aspects%20of%20life.%20Thus%2C%20the%20concept%20of%20the%20social-emotional%20learning%20division%20of%20Volanity%20was%20born%2C%20aiming%20to%20merge%20the%20practical%20and%20theoretical%20aspects%20of%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20understood%20that%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20solely%20depend%20on%20high%20school%20students%20to%20lead%20this%20division%20forward.%20%E2%80%9CA%20certain%20level%20of%20maturity%20is%20needed%20to%20teach%20these%20topics%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20This%20gave%20him%20the%20idea%20of%20approaching%20undergraduate%20students%20for%20the%20same.%20And%20Shoolini%20University%20%E2%80%94%20a%20private%20research%20university%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20was%20mo