ww.thebetterindia.com%2F281857%2Fupsc-cse-interview-topper-ias-apala-mishra-score-personality-test%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApala%20Mishra%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20secured%20AIR%209%20in%20UPSC%20CSE%20and%20got%20the%20highest%20marks%20in%20the%20interview%20round%2C%20says%20that%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20things%20to%20remember%20for%20the%20personality%20round%20is%20the%20DAF%20(Detailed%20Application%20Form).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CEnsure%20that%20you%20put%20in%20only%20those%20attributes%20and%20strengths%20that%20you%20wish%20to%20highlight%20in%20the%20DAF.%20Do%20not%20put%20down%20any%20achievements%20or%20hobbies%20that%20you%20cannot%20explain.%20The%20interviewers%20are%20likely%20to%20see%20through%20it.%20Revise%20whatever%20you%20have%20mentioned%20and%20have%20answers%20to%20everything%20you%20put%20down.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20go%20unprepared%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Apala%20says%20that%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20myths%20is%20that%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20interview%20round%20as%20it%20will%20only%20test%20your%20personality.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20we%20need%20to%20understand%20that%20knowledge%2C%20too%2C%20forms%20the%20basis%20of%20our%20personality.%20It%20requires%20equal%20amounts%20of%20work%20that%20one%20puts%20in%20at%20the%20prelims%20and%20mains%20stage%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Focus%20on%20what%20you%20know%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F281037%2Fhow-to-crack-upsc-interview-tips-ias-officer-twitter-personality-test%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJitin%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%202016-batch%20IAS%20officer%2C%20says%20that%20having%20confidence%20in%20what%20you%20already%20know%20is%20more%20important%20than%20wo