eading%5C%22%3E6.%20Be%20careful%20while%20responding%20to%20questions%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInterview%20is%20not%20a%20knowledge%20test%2C%20which%20has%20already%20been%20tested%20in%20the%20mains.%20Interview%20checks%20your%20personality%20traits%20via%20indirect%20methods%3B%20your%20response%20to%20questions%20will%20give%20them%20hints%20to%20assess%20your%20traits%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jitin.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E7.%20Keep%20your%20dress%20code%20simple%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20aspirants%20worry%20about%20what%20to%20wear%20during%20the%20personality%20test%2C%20IAS%20Jitin%20says%20that%20what%20you%20choose%20to%20wear%20does%20matter%20while%20appearing%20for%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20questions%20may%20come%20up%20regarding%20the%20brand%20or%20design.%20In%20my%20opinion%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20better%20to%20keep%20the%20outfit%20as%20simple%20as%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%237%20Optimum%20amount%20of%20nervousness%20is%20actually%20good%20for%20interview.%20If%20anxiety%20is%20in%20extremes%2C%20either%20too%20high%20or%20too%20low%2C%20then%20only%20it's%20a%20concern.%3Cbr%3E(Read%20Yerkes-Dodson%20Law%20%E2%80%93%20individual%20performs%20best%20with%20optimum%20amount%20of%20arousal)%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Jitin%20Yadav%20(%40Jitin_IAS)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJitin_IAS%2Fstatus%2F1508890232430637059%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2029%2C%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E8.%20Keep%20a%20check%20on%20your%20behaviour%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EJitin%20says%20that%20aspirants%20should%20never%20interrupt%20the%20board%20members%2C%20but%20instead%2C%20be%20open%20to%20being%20interrupted%20by%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20answer%20one%20question%20at%20a%20time.%20Never%20mix%20the%20previous%20question%20with%20the%20new%20one%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E9.%20Learn%20to%20manage%20anxiety%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EJitin%20says%20that%20an%20optimum%20amount%20of%20nervousness%20is%20actually%20good%20for%20the%20personality%20test.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20anxiety%20is%20in%20extremes%20%E2%80%94%20either%20too%20high%20or%20too%20low%20%E2%80%94%20only%20then%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20concern%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20suggests%20aspirants%20study%20Yerkes-Dodson%20Law%2C%20which%20explains%20how%20performance%20increases%20with%20physiological%20or%20mental%20arousal%2C%20but%20only%20up%20to%20a%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E10.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20be%20desperate%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EJitin%20emphasises%20that%20during%20the%20personality%20test%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20crucial%20to%20prioritise%20professional%20conduct%20over%20emotional%20reactions.%20%E2%80%9CNever%20show%20you%20are%20too%20desperate%20for%20getting%20selected%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699160520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2Fapala-2-1669797157.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D333542%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wondering%20how%20to%20do%20well%20in%20UPSC%20CSE%20interviews%3F%20IAS%20officers%20share%20golden%20tips%20to%20help%20you%20ace%20the%20personality%20test.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333542%2Fupsc-cse-interview-round-tips-by-ias-officers-personality-test-toppers%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%225%20Indian%20Entrepreneurs%20Earning%20Lakhs%20by%20Turning%20Trash%20to%20Treasure%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3