lb%20with%20a%20four-hour%20backup.%20But%20he%20wanted%20to%20provide%20an%208-10%20hour%20backup%2C%20which%20he%20was%20able%20to%20do%20thanks%20to%20computer%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20use%20a%20lithium%20ion%20battery%2C%20which%20has%20a%20backup%20of%20four%20hours.%20Now%2C%20I%20had%20to%20increase%20the%20backup%20time%2C%20without%20increasing%20the%20size%20of%20the%20cell.%20I%20applied%20the%20concept%20of%20control%20systems%20to%20increase%20the%20backup%20time.%20I%20did%20various%20trials%20using%20the%20pulse%20width%20modulation%20algorithm%20to%20achieve%20the%20desired%20result.%20This%20algorithm%20helped%20me%20optimise%20energy%20consumption%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20algorithm%20further%2C%20he%20says%20that%20he%20developed%20a%20way%20to%20adjust%20the%20bulb%E2%80%99s%20brightness%2C%20which%20extends%20the%20time%20of%20backup.%20If%20you%20lower%20the%20brightness%2C%20you%20get%20a%20longer%20backup.%20The%20bulb%20comes%20with%20settings%20to%20change%20the%20brightness.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20the%20bulb%20works%2C%20Uday%20states%20that%20the%20technology%20used%20is%20very%20simple.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20bulb%20is%20connected%20to%20a%20power%20source%2C%20energy%20gets%20stored%20in%20the%20battery.%20When%20the%20power%20supply%20is%20cut%20off%2C%20the%20bulb%20uses%20the%20energy%20stored%20in%20the%20battery%20to%20glow.%20I%20have%20done%20this%20using%20a%20rectifier%2C%20to%20make%20it%20glow%20during%20a%20power%20outage%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIlluminating%20over%207%2C000%20households%20in%205%20states%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20768px)%20100vw%2C%20768px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FUday3-2-1699023290.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22768%