the%20course%20of%20the%20walk%2C%20Pai%20gets%20asked%20about%20the%20%E2%80%9CChristmas%20trees%E2%80%9D%20that%20line%20the%20roads.%20He%20then%20stops%20and%20narrates%20how%20they%20came%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDid%20you%20know%20they%20are%20actually%20from%20New%20Zealand%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asks%20me.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%2060-foot%20trees%20are%20so%20prevalent%20these%20days%20that%20most%20people%20think%20they%20are%20native%20to%20the%20city.%20But%20it%20is%20interesting%20to%20know%20that%20they%20were%20brought%20here%20almost%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F182026%2Fmughal-miniatures-stunning-street-art-photo-story-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E200%20years%20ago%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20part%20of%20a%20massive%20botanical%20experiment%20by%20British%20and%20Indian%20scientists.%20They%20were%20trying%20to%20understand%20how%20to%20classify%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20trees%20and%20plants%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20city%20is%20not%20too%20high%2C%20not%20too%20low%2C%20not%20too%20wet%2C%20not%20too%20dry%2C%20it%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20conducive%20environment%20for%20these%20very%20foreign%20trees%20to%20grow.%20Today%20these%20%E2%80%98Christmas%20trees%E2%80%99%20(Norfolk%20Island%20Pines)%20have%20acclimatised%20to%20this%20climate%20and%20soil%20and%20have%20become%20local.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPai%20has%20narrated%20these%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F144331%2Fasi-finds-copper-bronze-age-chariots-tombs-up-village%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eother%20stories%20of%20the%20city%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20some%20of%20the%20most%20influential%20people%20%E2%80%94%20including%20global%20MD%20of%20McKinsey%20Dominic%20Barton%2C%20president%20of%20Microsoft%20Brad%20Smith%2C%20Infosys%20founder%20NR%20Narayanamurthy%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20Chief%20Economic%20Advisor%20Anantha%20Nageswaran%2C%C2%A0US%20Digital%20Ambassador%20Nathaniel%20Fick%2C%20former%20PM%20of%20Australia%20Kevin%20Rudd%20and%20comedian%20Trevor%20Noah.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20Nageswaran%20recounts%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20so%20happy%20that%20my%20friends%20from%20iSPIRT%20arranged%20for%20me%20to%20join%20Arun%20Pai%E2%80%99s%20Bengaluru%20walk%20on%2024%20July.%20He%20was%20simply%20brilliant%20with%20his%20erudition%2C%20wit%2C%20and%20deep%20understanding%20of%20the%20history%20of%20the%20world%2C%20the%20country%2C%20and%20the%20city.%20His%20pride%20in%20being%20a%20Bangalorean%20came%20through%20so%20well%20that%20I%20was%20infected%20with%20that%20pride.%20He%20made%20Sir%20M%20Visweswaraiya%20and%20the%20Mysore%20Maharaja%20come%20alive%20with%20his%20vivid%20descriptions%20of%20their%20vision%20and%20their%20contributions%20to%20the%20city%20and%20the%20country.%20It%20was%20a%20perfect%20start%20to%20the%20day%20and%20made%20my%20short%20visit%20to%20Bengaluru%20entirely%20memorable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20this%20adulation%2C%20one%20experience%20outshines%20it%20all%20%E2%80%94%20India%E2%80%99s%20Presidency%20of%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%202023.%20Karnataka%20played%20host%20to%20over%2010%20important%20summit%20meetings%20over%20the%20year%20including%20the%20G20%20Summit.%20And%20Pai%20was%20the%20official%20representative%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20Karnataka%20for%20designing%20and%20planning%20the%20city%20tours%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F127339%2Fcalcutta-houses-instagram-photo-project%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexcursions%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20last%20detail%20%E2%80%94%20including%20sites%20around%20cities%20like%20Mysuru%2C%20Hampi%2C%20and%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20experience%20at%20Hampi%2C%20Pai%20says%20it%20was%20phenomenal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20the%20course%20of%20the%20three%20days%2C%20I%20highlighted%20globally%20relevant%20stories%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20history%2C%20culture%20and%20society%20to%20over%20200%20delegates%C2%A0from%2020%20countries.%20We%20were%20given%20a%20clear%20task%20by%20Amitabh%20Kant%20%E2%80%94%20India%E2%80%99s%20Sherpa.%20He%20wanted%20us%20to%20provide%20the%20right%20context%2C%20background%20and%20experiences%20so%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F119531%2Fall-you-need-to-know-about-kashmirs-famous-pashmina%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esplendour%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20scale%20and%20sagacity%20of%20the%20Vijayanagar%20Empire%20could%20be%20effectively%20communicated%20to%20the%20high-empowered%20global%20audience.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20Pai%2C%20each%20walk%20is%20a%20creative%20utilisation%20of%20everything%20he%20has%20discovered%20about%20the%20city.%20He%20concludes%20by%20emphasising%20something%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20agree%20with%20more%20%E2%80%94%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20a%20heritage%20walker.%20I%20am%20India%E2%80%99s%20storyteller.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698999804000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWith-G20-Culture-Summit_11zon-1698934986.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D333441%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bengaluru's%20Arun%20Pai%20quit%20his%20corporate%20job%20to%20start%20%E2%80%98Bangalore%20Walks%E2%80%99%20and%20use%20storytelling%20to%20showcase%20the%20history%20and%20heritage%20of%20prominent%20Indian%20cities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A124%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UAW%20Deal%20With